											<div class=3D"entry-meta">
							<span class=3D"author vcard"><a href=3D"https://knitterskitchen.com/=
author/dieuwke/" title=3D"Knitting math: Re-calculating your size"><i class=
=3D"fa-regular fa-user"></i> dieuwke</a></span><span class=3D"posted-on"><a=
